1) ng new FoodOrder
2) ng serve --open
3) create components
      - ng g c navbar
      - ng g c footer
      - ng g c home
      - ng g c menu
      - ng g c about
      - ng g c contact

4) Path setting
      - go to app-routing.module.ts
            const routes: Routes = [
                --------   inside this set the path
            ];

5) app.component.html
      footer ans navbar router-outlet setting

6) go to navbar.component.html
      take a navbar code from the bootstrap
      After copying do the changes as we need
      Also give the style in navbar.component.css

7) Next go to footer.component.html  
      Create footbar design manually 
      take the social media icon from the bootstrap (first copy the icon link from the bootstrap and then copy it into the index.html)
      Then give the style in footer.component.css
      
8) Next create home page 
      take home.component.html
      create the design
      And give the style in home.component.css page

9) Create service folder(write click the app --> create folder -->services)
     command prompt cd copy path of service folder
     ng g s orderDetails

10) orderDetails.service.ts 
      create the food orderDetails

11) home.component.ts
      import OrderDetailsService
      inject the OrderDetailsService in constructor

12)home.component.html
       add the fooddetails to html    

13)Next Menu page
      menu.component.ts  -
            import OrderDetailsService
            inject the OrderDetailsService in constructor

      menu.component.html
            give the design 
            and set the style

14)menupage page
      menupage.component.ts  -
            import router
            inject the OrderDetailsService in constructor

      
     
